Homepage: https://gitlab.com/hamadmarri/gamma-text-editor
Description: Gamma (Î“) is a lightweight text editor. It is meant to be an alternative to Gedit or Notepad++. Lightweight, not CPU/RAM hungry. No learning curve (easy/familiar shortcuts, easy use of plugin/extensions). Fully customizable from A to Z (even the UI layout). New UX approach for text editors. Easy plugin system.
